{"tid":829153,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"喺餐廳見到一對母女","createTime":"2018-09-20T08:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T08:16:37.000Z","uid":70429,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"992f640c7770b9917d0fe8bda74348afe9b740f9","tid":829153,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:16:37.000Z","msg":"阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿媽（鄉音滿滿tone）:一陣個餐你自己拎啊！你已經大個！我幫唔到你一世架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我望一望佢個女，小學校服，大概小一小二咁。<br />\n<br />\n個餐出左，望一望個餐，熱辣辣沙沙聲嘅鐵板牛扒餐黎，個阿媽低緊頭玩電話。<br />\n個小朋友又真係行過去拎，但個經理唔比佢拎，叫個姐姐送過去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿媽:咁大個女連少少野都做唔到！點照顧自己啊！寵到壞曬！我好似你咁大果陣已經落田插秧啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （隻手不停咁督張枱）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不得不說阿樂嘅送餐服務真係窩心又體貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}